# assets/references/ -- local-only home for reference material (read-only, never a build input).
#
# An official place to keep project references and source clones used while working on this project
# -- e.g. the Stable Diffusion WebUI API docs, the original danbooru/artist tag-source dumps that
# `data/*.csv` were processed from, or any upstream prompt/list sources credited in
# `list-credits.md` -- so they have a known home and can be dropped back here if they ever get
# deleted, then referenced until they do.
#
# NONE of the contents are version-controlled (they can be large and are not ours to ship); only
# this .gitignore is tracked, which is what keeps the otherwise-empty folder in the repo.
*
!.gitignore
